            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Contribution of 184mRe production to the measured",
                "792 keV gammas was calculated by using the 184mRe",
                "production cross section determined by the 384 keV",
                "gammas. This showed that the 184gRe production",
                "contributes to the measured 792 keV gammas a few",
                "hundred times more than 184mRe production.",
                "Therefore it was assumed that 792 keV gamma is",
                "originated from 184gRe production."
